    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Protective screens made of woven or linked metal or other nonflammable material, placed in front of fireplace openings to prevent logs, sparks, or embers from escaping. For furniture used to protect occupants of the room from the full heat of the fire, use "fire screens (furniture)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
